S_n(x,a):=\displaystyle\sum\limits_{k=0}^{n}\binom{n}{k}a^k\cos(kx)
(1+z)^n=\sum_{k=0}^n\binom{n}{k}z^k
\displaystyle\sum\limits_{k=0}^{n}\binom{n}{k}a^k\cos(kx)=\displaystyle\sum\limits_{k=0}^{n}\binom{n}{k}a^k\Re(e^{ikx})=\Re\Big(\displaystyle\sum\limits_{k=0}^{n}\binom{n}{k}(ae^{ix})^k\Big)=\Re[(1+(ae^{ix}))^n]
